 \dfrac{d y}{dx}=\dfrac{y}{x}+1\quad\Longrightarrow\quad \frac{1}{x}\dfrac{d y}{dx}-\frac{1}{x^2}y=\frac{1}{x}\quad\Longrightarrow\quad \left(\frac{y}{x}\right)'-(\log x)'=0\quad\Longrightarrow\quad \frac{y}{x}=\log x+c, 
